    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "$$ \\text{连通块数量} = \\text{顶点数 (Vertices)} - \\text{边数 (Edges)} $$",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "所以总答案 = $\\sum$ <strong>(每个区间的顶点数 - 每个区间的边数)</strong>，",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "根据加法结合律，我们可以拆成两半算：",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "$$ \\text{总答案} = (\\text{所有区间里的顶点总数}) - (\\text{所有区间里的边总数}) $$",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "heading": "第一部分：算顶点的贡献",
          "level": 4,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "对于数字 $x \\in [1, N]$，它在多少个区间 $[l, r]$ 里出现？",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "只要 $l \\le x$ 且 $r \\ge x$，这个点就被算进去了。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "左端点 $l$ 的选择：$1 \\dots x$ （共 $x$ 种）",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "右端点 $r$ 的选择：$x \\dots N$ （共 $N - x + 1$ 种）",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>贡献值</strong>：$x \\times (N - x + 1)$",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "第二部分：算边的贡献",
          "level": 4,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "对于数组里的一条边 $(u, v)$ （即数组中相邻的两个数 $a_i, a_{i+1}$），它在多少个区间 $[l, r]$ 里是“有效”的？",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "边有效的前提是：<strong>两个端点</strong> $u$ <strong>和</strong> $v$ <strong>都在</strong> $[l, r]$ <strong>里</strong>。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "这意味着区间必须包裹住这两个数。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "设 $min\\_val = \\min(u, v)$，$max\\_val = \\max(u, v)$。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "条件变成了：$l \\le min\\_val$ 且 $r \\ge max\\_val$。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "左端点 $l$ 的选择：$1 \\dots min\\_val$ （共 $min\\_val$ 种）",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "右端点 $r$ 的选择：$max\\_val \\dots N$ （共 $N - max\\_val + 1$ 种）",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>贡献值</strong>：$min\\_val \\times (N - max\\_val + 1)$",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "void solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tll n; cin >> n;\n\tvar a = vector<ll>(n + 1);\n\tfa(i, 1, n)cin >> a[i];\n\tll ans = 0;\n\tfa(i, 1, n) // 枚举点\n\t\tans += a[i] * (n - a[i] + 1); // 点权贡献\n\tfa(i, 1, n - 1) { // 枚举边\n\t\tll u = a[i], v = a[i + 1];\n\t\tll mn = min(u, v), mx = max(u, v);\n\t\tans -= mn * (n - mx + 1); // 边权贡献\n\t}\n\tcout << ans << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
